Package: marchmadness2026
Title: 2026 NCAA March Madness Bracket Prediction System
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-03-16
Authors@R: person("verbologist", email = "user@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Predicts 2026 NCAA Men's and Women's March Madness tournament outcomes
    using an ensemble of logistic regression and XGBoost models trained on historical
    KenPom/BartTorvik efficiency metrics (2013-2025). Includes Monte Carlo bracket
    simulation (10,000 iterations) and a Shiny interactive bracket explorer.
    Methodology based on: arXiv:2603.10916 (CFA ensemble), arXiv:2503.21790
    (efficiency-based logistic regression), and Scheiner et al. (LSTM/Transformer).
Depends: R (>= 4.5.0)
